# PSR-4 Source Directory

This directory is ready for object-oriented class organization using the `Chubes\Extrachill\` namespace.

## Usage

Classes placed in this directory will be autoloaded via Composer:

```php
// Example: src/Services/AuthenticationService.php
namespace Chubes\Extrachill\Services;

class AuthenticationService {
    // Class implementation
}
```

```php
// Usage in theme files
use Chubes\Extrachill\Services\AuthenticationService;

$auth = new AuthenticationService();
```

## Directory Structure

Future object-oriented classes can be organized as:

```
src/
├── Services/        # Business logic services
├── Models/         # Data models  
├── Controllers/    # Request handlers
├── Utilities/      # Helper classes
└── Integrations/   # Third-party integrations
```